channel.title: Minecraft Realm - Finals are in! Vote for Japan or Ireland + UK!
channel.description:
Here is what every place looks like, incase you can't decide.
Hawaii - [IMG]http://i269.photobucket.com/albums/jj41/sarahfair_2008/hawaii-map.gif[/img]
Galapagos - [IMG]http://i254.photobucket.com/albums/hh101/bunghole112233/images2.jpg[/img]
Bahamas(Cuba not in pic, puerterico not in pic) - [IMG]http://i6.photobucket.com/albums/y242/Gomezy3k/BahamaIslandsMap.gif[/img]
Tazmania (it's the one island south of Australia) - [IMG]http://i291.photobucket.com/albums/ll286/mrclintontruong/RepublicofNewAlliedAustralia.png[/img]
Japan - [IMG]http://i297.photobucket.com/albums/mm204/tiajohn1987/japan_map.jpg[/img]
Madagascar - [IMG]http://i218.photobucket.com/albums/cc285/NeckCrackerSuite/aaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaamap.jpg[/img]
Iceland - [IMG]http://i38.photobucket.com/albums/e122/Furball279/Miscellaneous/europa-iceland.gif[/img]
Ireland + UK - [IMG]http://i208.photobucket.com/albums/bb35/rocket_058/UK-map.jpg[/img]
Sri Lanka - [IMG]http://i232.photobucket.com/albums/ee293/xochelseaaaa/sri-lanka-map.jpg[/img]
Taiwan - [IMG]http://i272.photobucket.com/albums/jj197/coki35vn/map_taiwan.jpg[/img]
New Zealand - [IMG]http://i71.photobucket.com/albums/i153/meggyslaughin/new-zealand-map2.jpg[/img]
Sizes given, pictures shown, vote away!!! The top for 4 go to a new poll, then, depending on how close it is will decide if a 1 on 1 is needed or a decision from those four.
